To stop all wars and move beyond violence, we need to establish that:

1. Nuclear bombs need to be disarmed everywhere, with everyone immediately;

2. All army bases, everywhere, need to be closed immediately;

3. Borders need to be opened everywhere. Visa not required to travel and live anywhere;

4. All the armies need to be abolished, as the concept of "divided world" has failed everywhere, and it is fundamentally anti-people, anti-life;

5. The primary model of economy needs to be "true cooperative", abandoning all kinds of monopolies everywhere;

6. The guiding principle of life needs to be traditional Golden Principal, found in every current of life, which says: "Treat Others As You would have them Treat You";

7. Human being to be the Highest and Central Value;

8. Non-violence as the fundamental method of Action. 

With these guiding principle, we can move beyond the stupidity of Individualism, Monopolies, Violence, Divide-&-Rule, that cause Discrimination, leading to Violence.

